Introduction

SUPER JUNIOR-L.S.S. (Korean: 슈퍼주니어-L.S.S.; Japanese: スーパージュニア-L.S.S.) is the sixth sub-unit of the South Korean boy group SUPER JUNIOR under SM Entertainment, Avex Trax and Label SJ. The unit consists of members Leeteuk, Shindong and Siwon.

The unit made their official debut on July 5, 2023 with the song "シャッター閉めろ" (Shatta Shimero), although had performed as a unit in previous concerts.
